# Constituent Part Proportion — SKOS ConceptScheme
# Generated from ConstituentPartProportions.xlsx
# Source sheets used: Concept Scheme, Concepts, Namespeces, Agents
# Generated: 2026-04-19

# Data issues / transformation notes:
#  1. The namespaces sheet is named "Namespeces" (typo for "Namespaces").
#  2. vocabularyIRI is <https://vocab.geospecimens.org/def/constituent-part-proportion>, but concept IRIs live under 2 distinct parent IRI(s):
#       - <https://vocab.geospecimens.org/def/constituent-part-proportion> (matches scheme)
#       - <https://vocab.geospecimens.org/def/constituent-part-proportions> (does NOT match scheme)
#     Transcribed as-written; reconcile in source if this is unintended.
#  3. The scheme-level skos:hasTopConcept cell contains 7 truncated or empty-slug URI(s) (e.g. ending in "/" with no concept slug). skos:hasTopConcept triples were instead derived from concept-level skos:topConceptOf values, which are complete.

# Standard prefixes
